org.jivesoftware.smack.sm.packet

Class StreamManagement.Enabled

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jivesoftware.smack.sm.packet.StreamManagement.Enabled
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Element, ExtensionElement, NamedElement, Nonza, TopLevelStreamElement
    Enclosing class:
    StreamManagement

    public static class StreamManagement.Enabled
extends Object
    A Stream Management 'enabled' element.

    Here is a full example, all attributes besides 'xmlns' are optional. 

     
 <enabled xmlns='urn:xmpp:sm:3'
      id='some-long-sm-id'
      location='[2001:41D0:1:A49b::1]:9222'
      resume='true'/>
